Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"

Type "chmod +x setup.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "./setup.sh help"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "clear"
Enter

Type "./setup.sh --macos --with-gnu --with-keyboard"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "clear"
Enter

Type "echo 'Setup Complete!'"
Enter
Sleep 2s
